headline: AMGEN'S LANDMARK PHASE 3 REPATHA DATA TO BE PRESENTED AS LATE BREAKER AT THE AMERICAN HEART ASSOCIATION SCIENTIFIC SESSIONS 2025
summary: Amgen (NASDAQ:AMGN) today announced that new data from its cardiovascular portfolio, including late-breaking results from the Phase 3 VESALIUS-CV clinical trial of Repatha® (evolocumab), will be presented at the American Heart Association Scientific Sessions taking place November 7-10, 2025, in New Orleans, LA.
